1.title: Life After Scientology

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

1.plot: In this season premiere, Leah and her family try group therapy to help navigate life after Scientology. Nanny Trish bravely tackles her final round of chemotherapy and Leah rallies to keep her spirits up.

2.title: Leah and Chelsea Handler's Dating Tips

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

2.plot: With the help of Chelsea Handler, Leah coaches her assistant Raffy on his dating skills when he lands a surprise date. After a makeover, a little waxing, and some blunt tips from Chelsea and Leah on talking to women; will Raffy's date be a success?

3.title: Bucket List

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

3.plot: Leah encourages mom Vicki to cross something off her bucket list - skydive! Trish and Angelo decide to join her, while the whole family goes to cheer them on. The night before, perhaps driven by the danger at hand, Angelo tries his hardest to seduce Leah.

4.title: I'm a Huge Star in Malaysia

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

4.plot: Leah discovers Angelo made a terrible commercial for the family's diner featuring zombies. Feeling inspired, he decides to film a brand new one. Meanwhile, Leah's assistant, Raffy, suggests she try auditioning for voice-over work, with hilarious results.

5.title: Happy Colonoscopy!

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

5.plot: Leah's stepfather, George, is turning 72 and the kicker is he's due for a colonoscopy the same week! Meanwhile, Leah and her family plan a memorable surprise birthday party but it does not go quite as planned.

9.title: Give It a Shot, Leah

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

9.plot: Leah prepares for a podcast with entertainer Michelle Visage, even though she's not exactly sure what it is. Meanwhile, the Remini clan go bowling, but the competition quickly spirals out of control.

10.title: The Dance Off

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

10.plot: Tony Dovolani makes a surprise appearance when Vicki challenges Leah to a dance-off at his studio. Angelo's son brings his newborn to the house for the first time, with Leah realizing she may now be known as "Grandma"!

11.title: Hmm, That's a Problem

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

11.plot: Leah plans a shopping trip for Sofia and two of her friends. Meanwhile, Shannon fields negative reviews at the restaurant, and the family discuss how to handle the criticism.

13.title: Weighting to Exhale

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

13.plot: Leah wants to lose weight and she challenges the women, plus Raffy, to see who can burn the most fat. Or, in Leah's case, who can FREEZE off the most fat! To get away from the stressed-out dieters, Sofia enjoys a very girly outing with Angelo and Lou.

14.title: The Camera Doesn't Lie

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

14.plot: Angelo surprises Leah with big ideas to redecorate their home, including a photo shoot to take new family portraits. However nothing goes as planned! Sofia's excited to update her bedroom, but her parents may not be ready for their little girl to grow up.

15.title: That's Life

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

15.plot: Sofia wants to cross two items off her living bucket list; the family anxiously waits to find out if Trish is cancer free; Vicki meets with a medium.

1.title: Welcome to the Family

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

1.plot: In the premiere of a reality series following the lives of actor Leah Remini and her inner circle, Leah and her husband, Angelo, plan a party for friends who supported them after leaving the Church of Scientology, but Angelo uses the event as an excuse to move Sofia's swing set out of the yard, an idea that doesn't sit well with Leah.

2.title: Putting the "Fun" in Funeral

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

2.plot: An argument goes too far and Leah's mom, Vicki, is left worrying how she'll be remembered when she dies. Competing to be 'favorite child,' Leah and sister Shannon agree to Vicki's morbid idea to hold a living funeral for her.

3.title: What's the Point, Mom?

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

3.plot: Mom Vicki decides she wants to spend more time with Leah. Leah is pre-occupied with decorating the restaurant, Vivian's, and takes the opportunity to kill two birds with one stone, enlisting her mother's help.

4.title: Lady Is a Tramp Stamp

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

4.plot: Leah's mom wants to spend more time with her, so Leah gets her to help decorate the restaurant.

5.title: Whole Lotta Shakin' Goin' On

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

5.plot: After an earthquake, Leah makes husband, Angelo, prepare the house for disasters. Meanwhile, Leah fears that nanny Trish's hobbies may be concealing a hoarding problem.

6.title: The Breast Birthday Ever

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

6.plot: When Shannon's 30th Birthday approaches, Leah and Vicki offer to fulfill her wish for a boob job. Vicki begrudgingly babysits for Sofia while Leah and Shannon go on a double date. Angelo and George shop for a boob shaped cake for Shannon's Birthday.

7.title: New York, New York Part 1

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

7.plot: Leah prepares for a trip to New York City, but first she has to pack for Angelo and Sofia while also trying to get over her fear of flying.

8.title: New York, New York Part 2

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

8.plot: Leah and Angelo tour New York City with Sofia to show her where they grew up. Meanwhile, Angelo secretly plans a reunion for Leah and her biological father; and in California, Vicki's dog creates chaos at Leah's house.

9.title: I Love You, Bra

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

9.plot: Leah asks Angelo to secretly follow Sofia on her Sacramento class trip to make sure she's safe. Meanwhile, Leah and Vicki teach Shannon how to be a better wife.

10.title: All Up in Your Grill

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

10.plot: Leah holds a cooking contest to see who gets the next special on the menu at Vivian's when she doesn't have a signature dish at the restaurant.

11.title: Let's Get Campy: Part1

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

11.plot: When Leah proposes a "girls road trip," Vicki suggests that they go camping instead. Leah is hesitant about the idea but agrees under the condition that they rent an RV for the trip. Meanwhile, the men plan to spend their time alone having a "mancation".

12.title: Let's Get Campy: Part 2

episode of.title: Leah Remini: It's All Relative (TV Series 2014– )

12.plot: Leah and the girls of the family are pleased to discover that instead of roughing it in the wilderness they will be glamour camping, or "glamping." Back at home, the men miss the girls and decide to give them a visit.
